ng-class-odd.

    - used to add the css classes to the odd rows of table.

ng-class-even.

    - used to add the css classes to the even rows of table.


Syntax.

    ng-class-odd / ng-class-even = "css class"


ng-if.

    used to write the if conditions in Angular Applications.

Syntax.

    ng-if="true" / "false"

ng-show / ng-hide.

    - used to show / hide the elements based on the conditions.

Syntax.

    ng-show / ng-hide = "true" / "false"

